name: ARE YA WINNING, SON?
description: ARE YA WINNING, SON? ($SON) is a whimsical Solana-based memecoin built around the legendary “Are ya winning, son?” meme. A 2014‐era MS Paint comic in which a father walks in on his son playing a hentai VR game and casually asks, “Are ya winning, son?” Ever since, the meme has evolved into a flexible template for gaming culture, parental poking fun, generational gaps and existential internet humor. $SON taps into that viral nostalgia with a tongue‑in‑cheek identity, offering the Solana community a humorous, low‑market‑cap token riding on meme momentum. Designed for meme collectors, gamers and crypto pranksters, $SON embraces irreverent fun while aiming to build virality-driven social traction—because at the end of the day: Dad, your $SON is winning.
